InfoTokens was written in Standard C (ISO/IEC 9899:1999) and should
build on any system with a compliant compiler. A Makefile is provided in
the source root directory of the release as a convenience.

To build this release of InfoTokens on your system use:

    # make

The main executable will be built in the current directory. To run use:

    # ./infotokens

To clean the directory of build files use:

    # make clean
